{"word":"G4837 - συμπαρακαλέω - symparakaléō - soom-par-ak-al-eh'-o - Comfort together","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμπαρακαλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">symparakaléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soom-par-ak-al-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Comfort together</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூட ஆறுதலடை"},{"paragraph":"1. to call upon or invite or exhort at the same time or together"},{"paragraph":"2. to strengthen (comfort) with others"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G3870 - παρακαλέω - parakaléō - par-ak-al-eh'-o/3870\">G3870</a>; to <i>console jointly:</i> - comfort together.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}